{"tid":546420,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"到底幾時用重有，幾時用仲用？","createTime":"2018-01-31T13:38:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T01:16:17.000Z","uid":111002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a94f7f50d433959407986e9b9355d8299cd40a70","tid":546420,"uid":111002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T13:38:26.000Z","msg":"屙緊屎嘅時候睇到個Post，見到肥絲捉人錯字<br />\n望到重有同仲有，其實應該係點用？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n定其實由頭到尾都無仲有嘅呢？"},{"pid":"8361918dd7f9e999ace18b21527815222539af5f","tid":546420,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T13:39:11.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"579cf1017f192c8395431b10d03fb08e5e3acf2b","tid":546420,"uid":111002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8361918dd7f9e999ace18b21527815222539af5f","tid":546420,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T13:39:11.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T13:41:17.000Z","msg":"我屙完屎了 <br />\n你重屌唔屌我老母？<br />\n你仲屌唔屌我老母？<br />\n邊個啱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3eac1b50080a4e12f6ab69cb21d63d9ee2ac95","tid":546420,"uid":40170,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T14:25:44.000Z","msg":"其實真係「重有」<br />\n重有更加更甚嘅引伸義<br />\n可以用嚟表程度<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n「舉立以為適而子之，夫在則重尊」<br />\n重就係「還更加」受尊敬<br />\n*呢句係出自史記呂不韋列傳<br />\n意思係如果華陽夫人將子楚立為世子 <br />\n因為佢本身無子 所以以子楚為其子就可以地位得到鞏固 還要更受尊敬<br />\n<br />\n利申 學渣"},{"pid":"3186c94619d845ab76a5100014fd9b75cae56bf9","tid":546420,"uid":164751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T14:32:38.000Z","msg":"官人我重要?<br />\nOr<br />\n官人我仲要?<br />\n未急屎但都諗緊"},{"pid":"3da6e0252cf71d802e7de6137aef451e86c803f6","tid":546420,"uid":111002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T01:16:17.000Z","msg":"肥絲呢？"}]}